@117011 = ~Shield of the Archons~
//
@11701 = ~Shield of the Archons
Level: 7
School: Abjuration
Sphere: Protection
Range: Personal
Duration: 1 turn
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

This abjuration causes any spells directed at the caster to be absorbed and consumed. This affects a total of 30 spell levels, meaning it can absorb 30 1st-level spells or 4 spells of 9th level or higher. Having one 'spell level' of protection left means a 1st level spell would get absorbed, as well as a 9th level spell. This spell will also protect the caster from Dispel/Remove Magic and Breach, while its protection lasts.

This spell absorbs magic effects cast from most scrolls and innate spell-like abilities, but will not protect against stationary area-effect spells such as Cloudkill or Stinking Cloud.

Shield of the Archons will block magic attacks under 5th level, such as Spell Thrust and Secret Word. A 6th-level or higher spell, such as Pierce Magic, is required to dispel it.
~
