@123021 = ~Remove Magic~
//
@12302 = ~Remove Magic
Level: 3
School: Abjuration
Range: Visual range of caster
Duration: special
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 15' radius
Saving Throw: None

This abjuration attempts to negate the magical combat protections and specific protections on enemies in the area of effect. It will dispel one combat protection and one specific protection from each such target. The targets' Magic Resistance, if any, does not affect this spell. 

The specific protection spells dispelled by Remove Magic include Chaos Shield, Chaotic Commands, Death Ward, Divine Protection, Emotion: Hope, Exaltation, Free Action, Greater Divine Protection, Impervious Sanctity of Mind, Improved Chaos Shield, Mind Blank, Mirrored Eyes, Protection from Acid, Protection from Cold, Protection from Divination, Protection from Electricity, Protection from Energy, Protection from Fire, Protection from Magic Energy, Protection from the Elements, Resist Elements, Resist Fear, Spirit Ward, Spiritual Clarity, Storm Shell, Storm Shield, and Unfailing Endurance. 

The combat protection spells dispelled by Remove Magic include Absolute Immunity, Armor of Faith, Barkskin, Circle of Bones, Cloak of Darkness, Emotion, Courage, Fire Shield, Iron Skin, Mage Armor, Mestil's Acid Sheath, Moment of Prescience, Physical Mirror, Protection from Magical Weapons, Protection from Missiles, Protection from Normal Weapons, Shield, Spirit Armor, and Stoneskin.
~
