Casting this spell will automatically create a Minor Spell Deflection and a Spell Deflection in addition to the Greater Spell Deflection. The lesser Deflection effects will not afford the caster additional 'spell levels' of protection - those from the lesser Deflections will be used up at the same time as those of this spell - but all three Deflection effects will independently protect the caster when they are subjected to magic attacks like Spell Thrust or Pierce Magic.

